  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when Jackson was appointed Chief of Council for War Crimes by President Truman, within a week, [CLEARS THROAT] Justice Jackson got the War Department to order Telford Taylor to come back and become one of his principal deputies.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And Taylor didn't even know why, but he was being shipped back to the States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and he became very-- immediately, one of the very close deputies to Justice Jackson.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I think that the trial-- the main-- the first trial had not been underway more than a month, before Jackson had it in his mind Taylor is the man I'm going to recommend to succeed me, to handle the next trials after the first trial.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Since I was the editor in chief of the official volumes on those trials, [COUGHS] I submitted them to-- I submitted drafts of some parts of those volumes to him, because he's a very great linguist, and he could improve, frankly, my diction.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And after I had finished [CLEARS THROAT] editing these volumes, or supervising the editing of them, General Taylor was made head of The Small Defense Plants Administration in about 1951.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the United States.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [CLEARS THROAT] he then called on me to become assistant administrator of the Small Defense Plants Administration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So by that time, I was done editing the trials and getting the publications, which you can see up here on the shelf-- 15 volumes, in those green volumes.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I moved over and became assistant administrator, under Telford Taylor, of the Small Defense Plants Administration.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Both.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] I was both in Nuremberg and in Washington.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
